**Event Title:** EVT - HackInTheBox  
**Event Description:** This is an evening hacker space at SAINTCON, operational after the main conference sessions. It provides facilities for soldering, presentations, networking, and contest collaboration. It has been running since 2016 and, while assisted by SAINTCON, is not an official event.  
**Organizers:** D4rkm4tter & Kampf  
**Operating Hours:**  
- Tuesday: 6:00 PM - 11:59 PM  
- Wednesday: 6:00 PM - 11:59 PM  
- Thursday: 6:00 PM - 11:59 PM  

**Website Links:**  
- Event URL: [Hack In The Box](https://saintcon.org/evt-hackinthebox/)  
- Registration: [Register Now!](https://saintcon.org/register/)  
- Download Wallpaper: [HITB Desktop Wallpaper](https://saintcon.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/HITB-2023_5K_Wallpaper.png)

**Additional Information:**  
HITB is described as a safe, welcoming space for conference attendees, serving as a favorite among keynote speakers. The event is located near the main venue.  
